        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Just as I architect systems for intelligence, I architect spaces in sound.
          Each composition is a journey through emotional and cognitive landscapes,
          designed to evoke specific states of consciousness.
        </p>
      </div>

